{"tid":1649672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乜都唔講，只係竟然有人可以喺燒衣隔離慶祝生日，都咪話唔佩服！","createTime":"2019-10-12T17:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T18:12:48.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"32e194d8b63dc47e3fbb4e0fb038117d8b251768","tid":1649672,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:59:01.000Z","msg":"其實如果你成班朋友，係抗爭既日子裏，Book咗酒店買埋個蛋糕，再係蛋糕上面寫着&lsquo;光復香港，時代革命&rsquo;，慶祝生日期間順便祝願抗爭成功係絕對冇問題！<br />\n<br />\n但唔係叫你起抗爭期間，係抗爭現埸，手足做緊嘢嘅時候，順便慶祝生日，你係同郭紹傑之流係一撚野！<br />\n<br />\n但退後一步，唔講策略立場分析等等，乜都唔講啦！<br />\n<br />\n我只係想問你一句，點解竟然有人會係燒衣嘅時候係隔離慶祝生日呢？？ <br />\n<br />\n你係咪弱智？ 係咪白癡呢？ 定係戇鳩？ 你有冇腦？？<br />\n定係你係警察派黎既臥底？事關你嘅智商同佢哋有得揮，<br />\n我哋有理由懷疑你係警察！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係覺得你好犀利，同Happy birthday to me有得揮！<br />\n簡直震驚30億人！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b1df37ea9a5b2c8634576fce15b146f7d243bd","tid":1649672,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55f49a8d640d48d89a6a0c27430968fde943b7b","tid":1649672,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:12:48.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討